high_descs: Head right to reach the dresser.
Pick up the knife from the dresser.
Turn right and head left to the room to face the shelf.
Cut the lettuce with the knife.
Turn around to reach the dresser.
Put the knife on the dresser.
Turn left to reach the shelf.
Pick up the slice of lettuce from the shelf.
Turn right to reach the fridge on the left.
Cool the slice of lettuce in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Put the slice of lettuce on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled slice of lettuce on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn right to reach the dresser under the TV.
Pick up the knife from the dresser.
Turn right and head down the passage on the left and reach the bedroom shelf on the right.
Cut the lettuce on the shelf with the knife.
Turn left to reach the dresser.
Put the knife on the dresser.
Turn around to reach the shelf.
Pick up the slice of lettuce from the shelf.
Turn right at the passage and head to the fridge on the left.
Cool the slice of lettuce in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to reach the dining table.
Put the slice of lettuce on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled slice of lettuce on the dining table.

high_descs: Walk straight and turn right to reach the dresser
Take a knife from the top of the dresser
Turn right and walks straight and turn left and take few steps and enter into first left side room and reach the rack
Cut the lettuce on the rack
Turn left and reach the dresser on the left side
Put the knife on the dresser
Turn towards back and reach the rack again
Take a lettuce piece from the cut lettuce
Turn right and walk out of the room. Then turn right and walk straight and turn left to reach the fridge
Open the fridge and put the lettuce piece inside it and close the door. After few seconds open the door and take the lettuce piece out and close the door again
Turn back and reach the dining table on the left side
Put the lettuce piece on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Put the lettuce piece on the dining table
